r fame made the name <i>Flora</i> popular in the Highlands and elsewhere."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Flor Felluca was born about 1230, in Italy as the daughter of Ricardo Felluca. She married Adonolfo Aquino in 1250. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died in 1296, at the age of 67."},"et":{"ABT 1230–1296":"umbes 1230–1296","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1218–1271":"1218–1271","1227–1283":"1227–1283","1200–Male":"1200–Surnud","1227":"1227","ABT 1230":"umbes 1230","1200":"1200","after 1283":"pärast 1283","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1250":"1250","1283":"1283","1271":"1271","1218":"1218","Kingdom of Naples":"Regno di Napoli","Italy":"Itaalia"},"fi":{"ABT 1230–1296":"noin 1230–1296","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1218–1271":"1218–1271","1227–1283":"1227–1283","1200–Male":"1200–Kuollut","1227":"1227","ABT 1230":"noin 1230","1200":"1200","after 1283":"1283 jälkeen","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1250":"1250","1283":"1283","1271":"1271","1218":"1218","Kingdom of Naples":"Regno di Napoli","Italy":"Italia"},"fr":{"ABT 1230–1296":"environ 1230–1296","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1218–1271":"1218–1271","1227–1283":"1227–1283","1200–Male":"1200–Décédé","1227":"1227","ABT 1230":"environ 1230","1200":"1200","after 1283":"après 1283","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1250":"1250","1283":"1283","1271":"1271","1218":"1218","Kingdom of Naples":"Regno di Napoli","Italy":"Italie","lifeSummary":"Flor Felluca est née environ 1230, à Italie, fille de Ricardo Felluca. Elle a épousé Adonolfo Aquino en 1250. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Elle est décédée en 1296, à l’âge de 67 ans."},"de":{"ABT 1230–1296":"um 1230–1296","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1218–1271":"1218–1271","1227–1283":"1227–1283","1200–Male":"1200–Verstorben","1227":"1227","ABT 1230":"um 1230","1200":"1200","after 1283":"nach 1283","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1250":"1250","1283":"1283","1271":"1271","1218":"1218","Kingdom of Naples":"Neapel","Italy":"Italien","lifeSummary":"Flor Felluca wurde um 1230 in Italien, als Tochter von Rica